# Settings › Rekrutacja

Block `LBL_RECRUITMENT` (`m260601_…_recruitment_settings_menu.php`). Submenus:

| View | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `Transitions` | Whitelist `u_yf_recruitment_status_transitions` + `u_yf_recruitment_settings.configured` |
| `Workflows` | Relation workflow badges / create links (`RelationTrigger`) |
| `TransitionMail` | Mail prompt matrix `u_yf_recruitment_status_transition_mail` |

Services: `RecruitmentStatusTransition`, `RecruitmentStatusTransitionMail` (multi-template rows per `from_status`/`to_status`). Save: `Settings\Recruitment\Actions\SaveAjax` (`saveTransitions`, `saveTransitionMail`).

## Mail-on-transition (runtime)

- **Trigger:** kanban drag only, after successful `changeStatus()`.
- **Templates:** `ProjektyRekrutacyjne` module list; modal filters via `templateIds` on `IndividualSendMailModal` + `Vtiger.js` `triggerSendEmailModal`.
- **Gates:** `MassComposeEmail` on Kandydaci, `isActiveSendingMails`, default SMTP, candidate has email (`RelatedListLeftSideEmail::recordHasEmail`).

## TransitionMail matrix UI

- Per cell: checkbox → show `.js-mail-template-wrap` (hide when unchecked); template `<select multiple>` inside wrap only if `TEMPLATE_OPTIONS` non-empty.
- Init Select2 with `select2noactive` + `app.showSelect2ElementView($select, { placeholder: '\u00a0', tags: false })` then clear `.select2-selection__placeholder` text — avoids `JS_SELECT_SOME_OPTIONS` default for bare `multiple` selects (`app.js` ~259).
- Do not use `LBL_MAIL_PROMPT_TEMPLATES` as visible placeholder.

Smoke: `docker compose exec -T app php tests/recruitment_status_transition_mail_smoke.php`
